PrecisAmendments to the GOVERNMENT PROPERTY TRAFFIC REGULATIONS which increase the fines for parking violations from $7.00 to $25.00 and establish a fine of $50 for parking in a spot designated for handicapped drivers only.

precis:
Amendments to the GOVERNMENT PROPERTY TRAFFIC REGULATIONS which increase
the fines for parking violations from $7.00 to $25.00 and establish a fine
of $50 for parking in a spot designated for handicapped drivers only.
